dct_title_s: Prof. C. Haussknecht's Routen im Orient, 1865-1869
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading. Includes insets. Map III has insets: Route in Nord-Persien -- Türkisch-Persicher Grenzbezirk in Kurdistan im doppelten Massstab der Hauptkarte -- Der mittlere Theil der Hauptkarte in doppeltem Massstabe. Historic Maps copy imperfect: Maps I-II and IV, and text, wanting.
